<eesti> on asjakohane, et p&auml;dev asutus v&otilde;iks p&auml;rast riski hindamist ohtlikust ainest teavitanule oma j&auml;reldustest teada anda ja et ta seej&auml;rel saadaks vastava kirjaliku aruande komisjonile; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas it is appropriate to reduce to a minimum the number of animals used for experimental purposes in accordance with Council Directive 86/609/EEC of 24 November 1986 on the approximation of the laws, regulations and administrative provisions of the Member States regarding the protection of animals used for experimental and other scientific purposes (3); </inglise>
